title: #339: #FreeBritney Swapcast With Jay Dyer, Issac Weishaupt and Chrissie Mayr
description:

Tin Foil Hat Podcast Live at the World Famous Comedy Store July 18th at 8pm. Come watch for free on the patio of the Greatest Comedy Club ever.
